{"tid":1696133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後所有活動係咪應該好似尋日V煞日咁搞?","createTime":"2019-11-06T04:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T05:24:04.000Z","uid":61743,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3190b690f3f8d73d37d0974ff723f43d3436fb","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"尋日活動證明唔使預先公報地點, 都可以召集到咁多人參加, 亦都唔算多人被拉。除左狗屋附近, 睇到尖沙咀要差唔到9:00開始(時間有錯請更正)先多狗, 即係要一個鐘先組織到, 正常即走又冇行錯路既話理論上有足夠時間散水, 再加彩虹戰衣更加可以掩飾下。<br />\n<br />\n除左民陣搞既遊行集會, 以後所有活動係咪都唔應該再預先公報活動地點, 縮短啲狗佈防時間，減低被拉機會? 大家討論下可行性。"},{"pid":"2c0767f30d22cd04a10cb93320514a70cff0a0b9","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f408b5aa0d8a02e2db5b70b484e6eb424d5ed054","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43ad5e773228d2c03fee288d60373a1df82121f0","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fb9ac2cb7ca8910d24be3c73a155f7823deff6a","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6411af4349ee99c60cf809df939eccef49b3701","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72379580bd2c79585b46cbf78256014d15fec62b","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d6e77b421ec5d233cc94822edb06fecfea0dc39","tid":1696133,"uid":61743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"755212f58f7181dca2a90ac424507283b47b3085","tid":1696133,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"係啊<br />\n如果喺愈接近嘅時間講<br />\n佢調兵要出車就一定搞到全香港都好緊張"},{"pid":"088e72b476824790e